Package net.tnemc.core.manager

Class TransactionManager

java.lang.Object
net.tnemc.core.manager.TransactionManager
public class TransactionManager extends Object
Manages everything related to the transaction system. This is usually just keeping track of the various check types and other systems.
Since:
0.1.2.0
